<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.4.2">
<l>kuṟṟamiṉṟik kuṇamperukkiku rukkaḷukkaṉu kūlarāy</l>
<l>ceṟṟamoṉṟumi lātavaṇkaiyi ṉārkaḷvāḻtiruk kōṭṭiyūr</l>
<l>tuṟṟiyēḻula kuṇṭatūmaṇi vaṇṇaṉtaṉṉait toḻātavar</l>
<l>peṟṟatāyarva yiṟṟiṉaipperu nōyceyvāṉpiṟan tārkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirukkōṭṭiyūr dwell those with generous hands,</l>
<l rend="indent">who are without hatred for anything,</l>
<l>being blessings to the gurus,</l>
<l rend="indent">increasing [their] faultless excellence,</l>
<l>[and] there are those who do not worship him</l>
<l rend="indent">with the pure jewel hue, who seized the seven worlds</l>
<l rend="indent">with [his] mouth and consumed [them],</l>
<l>who were born to cause great suffering</l>
<l rend="indent">to the bellies of the mothers who begot [them].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
